snippet.title: Two Handed Mage - Trailer
snippet.description:
Free download: https://yojka27.itch.io/thm

You can also follow us:
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/Q4Hsrp4h63
Telegram: https://t.me/thmproject
VK: https://vk.com/thmproject
Feel free to ask any questions :)

Two Handed Mage is a fast-paced arena roguelike shooter in which deep deck-building is faced with fast-paced tactile gameplay. It is still under development, stay tuned on our pages!

Music by Audionautix.com (remixed by me)
